---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  current=""
  title="Privacy Policy | RRS Realty Group"
  description="How RRS Realty Group collects, uses, and protects the information you share when you request to be matched with a local real estate agent."
>
  <section class="page-head">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>How we handle the information you share with us.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top:36px">
    <div class="prose">
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>

      <p>RRS Realty Group ("we," "us") operates RRSRealtyGroup.com. This policy explains what we collect and how we use it. By using this site or submitting our form, you agree to the practices described here.</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you fill out our matching form, we collect the details you provide, such as your name, ZIP code, email address, phone number, and any notes about your move. We may also collect basic, non-identifying analytics about how visitors use the site (such as pages viewed) to help us improve it.</p>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information you submit for one primary purpose: to match you with a vetted local real estate agent and to follow up about your request. We share the details you provide with the agent we match you with so they can contact you. We do not sell your personal information.</p>

      <h2>Communication</h2>
      <p>By submitting the form, you consent to be contacted by RRS Realty Group and your matched agent by email, phone, or text regarding your request. You can opt out of further communication at any time by letting us know.</p>

      <h2>Data Retention and Security</h2>
      <p>We retain your information only as long as needed to provide our service and meet legal obligations. We take reasonable measures to protect it, though no method of transmission over the internet is completely secure.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use trusted third-party tools to operate the site and process form submissions. These providers handle data on our behalf and are expected to protect it.</p>

      <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p>We use a minimal amount of cookies and similar technologies to make the site work and to understand, in aggregate, how it's used. We do not use cookies to sell your information or to serve targeted advertising. For details and how to control cookies, see our <a href="/cookies/">Cookie Policy</a>.</p>

      <h2>Do Not Sell My Information</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information, and we do not share it for cross‑context behavioral advertising. We share the details you submit only with the agent(s) we match you with so they can contact you about your request.</p>

      <h2>Your Privacy Rights</h2>
      <p>Depending on where you live, you may have the right to access, correct, or delete the personal information you've submitted, and to opt out of certain processing. To make a request, email us at <a href="mailto:rrsrealtygroup@gmail.com">rrsrealtygroup@gmail.com</a> and we'll respond as required by applicable law. Where required, we honor browser Global Privacy Control (GPC) signals.</p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>The site is intended for adults and is not directed to children under 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided us information, contact us and we will delete it.</p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with a revised date.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this policy? Email us at <a href="mailto:rrsrealtygroup@gmail.com">rrsrealtygroup@gmail.com</a>.</p>

      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2em"><em>This template is provided for convenience and is not legal advice. Consider having an attorney review it for your specific situation and any state requirements.</em></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
